# UX: rc=4 (ran but errored) no longer points a device user at a log file they cannot read.
desc Sync now rc=4 maps to an actionable message, not "see last-sync.log"
config paired
seeded
pick 0|Sync now
pick 2|
engine 4|
expect_exit 0
expect_log err: Sync finished with errors - some items didn't sync, try again
